name: Teacups
description:
Introduction

A great canyon to practice pothole escapes, even though many of the potholes can be walked around. Wetsuits recommended during cold weather. Water anchor, SandTrap, and pothole escape gear recommended.

Approach

Descent

Exit

Red tape

Permit required from the Navajo Nation.
